msgid "Zeina Abi Assy Mozilla Festival Director - speaking on stage at MozFest - Zoomed in"
msgstr "Zeina Abi Assy Mozilla, Dyrektor Festiwalu – wystąpienie na scenie MozFest – przybliżone"

msgctxt "body.c2b6757e-6498-4d12-b784-0da975b7e7c7.right_column.fb4ec021-7995-4805-b207-4aa4bfb83589.quote"
msgid "At MozFest, Wilding is an invitation to restore balance: cultivating infrastructures rooted in care, mutuality, and collective action."
